|               |                                   TableScan: date_dim projection=[d_date_sk, d_date], partial_filters=[date_dim.d_date >= Date32("1999-05-01"), date_dim.d_date <= Date32("1999-06-30")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
