|               |                       Projection: call_center.cc_call_center_sk                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |                         Filter: call_center.cc_county IN ([LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County")])                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                           TableScan: call_center projection=[cc_call_center_sk, cc_county], partial_filters=[call_center.cc_county IN ([LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County"), LargeUtf8("Williamson County")])]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
